# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  Office Power Monitor — Root .env.example
#  Copy each section into the relevant workspace .env
#  or set them in your deployment environment.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Backend (backend/.env) ──────────────────────────────
PORT=4000
HOST=0.0.0.0
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

# Simulator
SIMULATOR_TICK_MS=5000
MIN_DWELL_SECONDS=60

# Office hours (24h format)
OFFICE_HOUR_START=9
OFFICE_HOUR_END=17

# Alert threshold: entire room on for >N hours triggers high alert
ROOM_ON_MAX_HOURS=2

# ── Frontend (frontend/.env) ────────────────────────────
VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:4000

# ── Discord Bot (bot/.env) ──────────────────────────────
# Required
DISCORD_TOKEN=your-bot-token-here

# Backend connection
BACKEND_HTTP_URL=http://localhost:4000
BACKEND_WS_URL=http://localhost:4000

# Optional: comma-separated channel IDs that receive live alert posts
ALERT_CHANNEL_IDS=

# Optional: OpenAI for polished natural-language responses
OPENAI_API_KEY=
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
